text: Desmiphora lenkoi is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Lane in 1959. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Desmiphora lenkoi. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. It feeds on the willow-leaf red quebracho. ==References== Category:Desmiphora Category:Beetles described in 1959
